title: John Wayne | The Trail Beyond (Western, 1934) directed by Robert N. Bradbury

sources.title: John Wayne | The Trail Beyond (Western, 1934) directed by Robert N. Bradbury
sources.description:
WHERE LIFE WAS RAW AND MIGHT WAS LAW! 
John Wayne embarks on a perilous quest to uncover the truth behind a missing girl, ultimately facing off against lethal foes and discovering a long-hidden fortune in a secluded valley 

Watch original B&W version: https://youtu.be/N_MVuinVf50

Director: Robert N. Bradbury
Writers: James Oliver Curwood (novel The Wolf Hunters), Lindsley Parsons
Stars: John Wayne, Noah Beery, Verna Hillie 
Genre: Colorized movie, Western, Action, Adventure, Drama

This video is subtitled in more than 30 languages. Click on ⚙️ and choose subtitles and/or audio tracks.
